wiki.summary: On “HeMotions,“ Juice WRLD takes a more positive outlook than that which he is usually known for, detailing the way he lives his life, going through the motions, while hoping (and trying to gain) a happier future with his significant other. “HeMotions” is a pun on the words “he” and “emotions,” perhaps implying that emotions are seen as innately feminine. The original demo of "HeMotions", titled "The Motions had Ty Dolla $ign featured on the track. Read more on Last.fm.
